Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: South Africa boycott
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xl0t
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 28 Jul 1985
Zulu chief Buthelezi wades US row over South Africa business boycott. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.